          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1635255002849-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1635255002849-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1635255002849-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>sliced radishes</strong>, <strong>sliced cucumber</strong> and <strong>carrot ribbons</strong> in a bowl with <strong>half </strong>of the <strong>Vietnamese-style marinade</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>crunchy salad</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>remaining Vietnamese-style marinade </strong>and <strong>chopped pork</strong> to a bowl and mix until fully combined</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1635255009107-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1635255009107-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1635255009107-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1635255009107-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1635255009107-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>marinated pork</strong> along with any <strong>remaining Vietnamese-style marinade</strong> from the bowl and cook for 7-8 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>Vietnamese-style pork</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1635255015624-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1635255015624-x400.jpg",
